CHANGELOG
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5 - May 22, 2013
* About button added.

Version 0.0.4 - May 13, 2013
* Split the code into multiple files. Changed some comments.

Version 0.0.3 - May 13, 2010
* Now uses libtotem 2.30 instead of 2.28. 2.28 may still be used with slight
  modifications to the code.

Version 0.0.2 - May 6, 2010

* Fixed some issues with the volume slider page increment size.
* Fixed some compatibility issues with Windows.


Version 0.0.1 - April 22, 2010

* Birth of GTK Media Box with all intended features implemented.
